comments.text:
Sup everyone! Tamers12345 here with a very special video today. Now, I've been watching to make this video and I've been wanting to make this video for a very long time, addressing what people are saying about my accent or my voice or whatever the hell you wanna call that bitch. And...and... and it's gotten to the point where people are bullying me and shit, like I don't give a FUCK what you think! People...people are like "Tamers, what is your accent. Like..are you...are you white, are you black, like like, are you, are you Australian or some shit?" BITCH  I...SHUT THE FUCK UP...BIIIITCH. Like, my mama told me people tell me all the time that I sound like Obi-Wan Kenobi from Star Wars. Just last week my mama was like "BITCH you sound like [???]" like like...I don't know why people think...people...it got to the point to it's bad. People will say "Your voice is STOOOPID" people think it's like...like...people think I'm trying too hard to sound ghetto.

I mean shit, like, you you live in the ghetto for five minutes and see how YOUR voice turns out. Like maybe I DID grow up in the ghetto. Maybe I'm retarded bitch. Like, maybe YOUR retarded, biiiitch biiiiiitch. Like, you you don't control me, you're a little bitch! Like your...like if if you think my accent is stupid, I think you're a little fucking bitch.You can KISS MY ASS. BITCH. I mean shit, like like like I sometimes I even get like 10, 20 maybe even 30 comments a day of people saying like "Your voice is STOOOPID". Well, you know what I say to that? I say all 45 of you bitches, your voices are stupid. You guys are all in the comment sextons...sections and shit and and have you heard your voices? Fuck no! FUCK NO! You haven't heard each other's voices. So just because I'm more famous than you, you think you have the right to say that you're- MY VOICE IS STUPID? My mama says I sound like [???] bitch. Do you sound like [???] ? No you don't. Do you like like Obi-Wan? NO! You bitches sound like the Yoda, you pickin' up on what I'm putting down bitches? You pickin' it up? PICK IT UP. Bend over and P I C K  IT  U P BITCH, or I will KICK YOUR ASS.

What I'm saying bitches is don't...do not make people....put people down just because you think their voice is better than yours, okay? Do...Are we clear here? I think we are. Cause if not, I think we're gonna have a problem. Do you underSTAND? Another thing, people like to say "Tamers, why do you say 'and shit' at the end of every phrase and shit?" Like...like for example I say last week I was walking  down the street and I saw and I met a Sonic Underground fan so you know what I did? I beat his ass and shit. People say why do you add the phrase 'and shit' at the end? And you know why? Because I'm never done. I'm never done bitches. Like when, if I saw 'and shit' you do not know what I'm gonna say next. You know why? Because I...I am like the only Sonic Underground fan left and shit and I am doing whatever I can to bring back Sonic Underground. 

So...so people they look at me and think 'Wow, Tamers that guy is amazing and shit. He's like...you just don't know what he's gonna do next. He's crazy, like like that's what I like.'  Unlike you all, you like to say that I'm the crazy one, fuck NO BITCH. Like I am normal. If anything you're the normal one's and me being weird makes me different and different is good. Do you understand, or are you poopy baby bitches? Do you need me to change your t'diaper, you poopy baby bitches? Is that too hard for you to understand? Is that..is that why? Because you're literally poopy baby bitches who  are afraid of shit you don't understand? WE LIVE IN A SOCIETY where people are afraid of what they don't understand and because of that even if somebody has a different voice than them and shit, they're like, "I don't like that person". Well you know what, bitch? I don't like YOU. Nobody likes YOU. Everybody hates YOU bitch. You wanna know why everybody hates YOU? Because...because you're normal, and normal is bad, bitch. 

Sorry about cutting off like that, I had to poop a little bit. Anyways, back to what I was saying...what was I saying again? OH YEAH. One thing about this world that makes it good is that some people have different voices and shit. For example, let's say you go into a Taco Bell, like...like if it you're basically stepping through Mexico at that point and...and odds are...like you bash me about my voice...yet yet if you step into a Taco Bell odds are...you will learn at least 2-3 Mexican words like like in an instant. Like like like you'll like you'll learn the word taco, you'll you'll learn burrito. Like like the the cup sizes are small, medium, and grande. Do you know what grande is, bitch? Like uhm, that's Mexican...that's Mexican like big or some shit. Like...I dunno I don't give a fuck.

Anyways that's all I wanted to say.
